Class COMInputFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • COMInputFile

  • public class COMInputFile
extends java.lang.Object
    This class manages output to a .com file for MacroModel conformational search. The class itself only stores the associated catalyst, but the write method will write the parameters necessary to run a conformational search. See the main program class for organization of input and output files.
